1) BAI TOAN MA BAI BAO GIAI QUYET
- Bai bao giai bai toan dac trung hoa tinh toan luong tu thoi gian da thuc (FBQP/BQP) bang mot mo hinh thu ba, khong dung truc tiep QTM hay ho mach luong tu.
- Mo hinh thu ba la mot dinh nghia so do (schematic definition) cua ham luong tu tren H_infty, gom:
  + Ham khoi tao: I, NOT, PHASE_theta, ROT_theta, SWAP, MEAS.
  + Quy tac xay dung: Compo, Branch, kQRec.
- Dinh ly chinh (Theorem 4.1): lop ham square_1^QP (dac biet la mu square_1^QP khi bo MEAS) dac trung dung cac ham trong FBQP theo nghia xac suat thanh cong cao.
- Nghia la: co tuong duong ly thuyet giua mo hinh so do ham luong tu va mo hinh may/mach luong tu de mo ta tinh duoc da thuc.

2) CACH TIEP CAN CUA BAI BAO KHAC GI SO VOI CAC CACH TRUOC (UU/ NHUOC)

2.1) So voi QTM
- QTM can dieu kien well-formedness (unit length, orthogonality, separability) de dam bao unitarity.
- Cach tiep can moi tranh duoc viec phai dat va kiem tra truc tiep cac dieu kien ky thuat nay trong mo hinh may.

Uu diem:
- Don gian hon ve mat mo ta: "xay ham" thay vi "dinh nghia ham chuyen may".
- Co tinh mo-dun: ghep quy tac de tao ham lon tu ham nho.
- Voi lop mu square_1^QP, co tinh dong duoi phep nghich dao (Proposition 3.5).

Nhuoc diem/chi phi:
- Chung minh tuong duong voi QTM rat ky thuat (Lemmas 4.2, 4.3; Section 5).
- Can ma hoa chi tiet ky hieu bang va cau hinh (hat(0), hat(1), hat(b), hat(2), hat(3)).
- Can them workspace/padding do ham trong mu square_1^QP bao toan so chieu.

2.2) So voi quantum circuits
- Ho mach luong tu can uniformity condition de mo ta ho mach kha lap trinh theo n.
- Cach tiep can so do khong can dua ra uniformity theo kieu ho mach; qua trinh xay ham chinh la dac ta hanh vi.

Uu diem:
- Xu ly dau vao so qubit tuy y (khong bi co dinh theo tung mach don le).
- Tu nhien cho nghien cuu descriptional complexity (do phuc tap mo ta).
- Co the dien dat cac cong/chuyen doi quan trong (CNOT, WH, CPHASE, QFT co dinh k).

Nhuoc diem:
- Ngon ngu ky hieu va de quy luong tu (kQRec) co do phuc tap cao, kho doc voi nguoi moi.
- Mot so phep bien doi tong quat (vi du QFT tren so qubit tuy y) co the can mo rong tap ham khoi tao (Section 6.1, vi du CROT).

3) CAC LINH VUC CO THE AP DUNG PHUONG PHAP TRONG BAI BAO
- Ly thuyet do phuc tap luong tu:
  + Tao thang do descriptional complexity dc(f)[n] cho ham/ngon ngu.
- Descriptional complexity va phan loai bai toan:
  + So sanh suc manh mo ta cua ngon ngu/ham theo do dai dau vao.
- Ly thuyet ham bac cao (higher-type quantum functionals):
  + Mo rong type-1 sang type-2 voi oracle (Section 6.3, QUERY).
- Nen tang logic/ly thuyet bac nhat cho tinh toan luong tu:
  + Dinh huong xay first-order quantum theories (Section 6.2).
- Thiet ke ngon ngu lap trinh luong tu:
  + Dinh nghia so do co the xem nhu chuong trinh xay ham; hop cho DSL/QLang (Section 6.4).
- Ky thuat mo phong va bien doi:
  + Encoder/Decoder va copy thong tin co dien da ma hoa (Lemmas 5.1, 5.2) co gia tri trong pipeline xu ly du lieu luong tu-co dien.

4) SO SANH VOI CAC PHUONG PHAP HIEN NAY

4.1) Voi khung ly thuyet chuan (QTM + circuits)
- Bai bao khong thay the hoan toan QTM/circuits trong trien khai, nhung dua ra mot mo ta tuong duong ve mat suc manh tinh toan (Theorem 4.1).
- Gia tri noi bat:
  + Goc nhin "xay dung ham" thay vi "thiet ke may/mach".
  + Giam phu thuoc vao dieu kien ky thuat nang (well-formedness, uniformity) o cap mo hinh.

4.2) Voi nhu cau thuc te hien nay (NISQ, framework lap trinh)
- Thuc te he sinh thai hien tai van xoay quanh circuit model va compiler stack.
- Phuong phap trong bai phu hop hon voi:
  + Nen tang ly thuyet.
  + Kiem chung tinh tinh toan.
  + Thiet ke ngu nghia/ngon ngu lap trinh cap cao.
- Chua phai mot quy trinh thay the truc tiep cho flow transpiler-hardware, nhung la co so manh de xay abstraction cap cao.

4.3) Tong ket so sanh
- QTM/circuit: manh o mo phong thuc thi va he cong cu co san.
- Schematic square_1^QP: manh o tinh khai niem, tinh mo-dun, kha nang mo rong sang do phuc tap mo ta, logic va ham bac cao.
- Vi tri hop ly hien nay: bo sung va tang cuong ly thuyet cho cac phuong phap chuan, khong doi khang.

